flowchart TD
    A[Select highest-priority unblocked item] --> B[P1: Request lifecycle protections]
    B --> C[Implement in-flight guards in App.tsx]
    C --> D[Load action: immediate lock via ref]
    C --> E[Run action: immediate lock via ref]
    D --> F[Only related control disabled]
    E --> F
    F --> G[Add interaction tests in App.test.tsx]
    G --> H[Disable/re-enable lifecycle tests]
    G --> I[Rapid repeated click/submit lockout tests]
    G --> J[Failure then same-session retry success test]
    H --> K[Fresh docker reset/build/up]
    I --> K
    J --> K
    K --> L[Health + backend tests + frontend tests + typecheck + build passed]
    L --> M[Blocked external dependency?]
    M -->|No| N[Update IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md and finish loop artifacts]
